      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still bothering with the lab reports. everything is just... gone. the funding got pulled, the data was a mess, and i feel like there's literally nothing left of me outside of this degree. i'm just so incredibly tired of existing in this loop. i just want to sleep and never have to wake up to this pressure again.",
