      "content": "It sounds like you're desperate for a way out, and you're willing to do whatever it takes to escape the cycle of suffering. While it's great that you're recognizing your feelings and willing to confront them, it's understandable that you're unsure of how to move forward. Many people have felt this way, and it's often a matter of finally accepting the reality that they can't change the situation or find a way out on their own. In this case, it might be helpful to explore what you truly want from life and work, and to consider whether you're being truly fulfilled in your current circumstances.",
